http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Mangalore/Corporation-Bank-gets-new-ED/article14015826.ece

The Union government has appointed Sunil Mehta as the Executive Director of Corporation Bank. Mr. Mehta took the charge on Friday.An official release here said that Mr. Mehta is a postgraduate in agriculture, besides the Masters in Business Administration and Certified Associate of Indian Institute of Bankers. Prior to this appointment, Mr. Mehta was general manager of Allahabad Bank.He carries with him a wide banking experience spanning more than 33 years. He was holding important assignments of zonal head and field general manager in Allahabad Bank.